&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Virtru:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;While the rest of the security industry obsesses over locking data down to prevent it from being lost or stolen, we&#39;re doing something fundamentally different at Virtru. We&#39;re setting data free so that you can intentionally share it with others, but without sacrificing security, privacy, or control.&lt;/p&gt;
